words with a-position counts `{4, 1, 4, 1}`, summing to 10 telescoping
summands. Each summand has the form `[product]·(z−x)·[product]` with the
products totaling 4 letters from `{x, z, y}`; bounded by M⁴·‖z−x‖. -/
