Foundation for stepping stone 1 (`symmetric_bch_septic_sub_poly_axiom`
discharge): with `z = (a'+b) + W` and `‖W‖ = O(s²)`, gives an
O(s⁸·‖W‖) bound on `‖Z₇(z, y) − Z₇(a'+b, y)‖`. -/

